</div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">External Links</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>TinySorted may contain links to external websites.</p><p>We are not responsible for the content, policies, or practices of third-party websites.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Affiliate Relationships</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>Some articles contain affiliate links.</p><p>Purchases made through these links may generate a small commission that supports TinySorted.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Disclaimer</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>The information published on TinySorted is intended for educational and informational purposes only.</p><p>Readers should exercise their own judgment before making purchasing or organizational decisions.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Limitation of Liability</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>TinySorted shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages resulting from the use of this website.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Changes to These Terms</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>We reserve the right to modify these Terms &amp; Conditions at any time.</p><p>Updated versions will always appear on this page.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Contact</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>Questions regarding these Terms &amp; Conditions may be sent to:</p><p class=\"mt-6 font-medium\">